📌 Chat Smart
💬 Chat Smart – TCP Based GUI Chat Application

Chat Smart is a desktop chat application developed using TCP Socket Programming for Computer Networks major project.
It provides real-time messaging with an attractive GUI interface similar to modern messaging apps.


Chat Smart is built using the TCP protocol to ensure reliable communication between clients and server.
The application includes a splash screen, user selection, message bubbles, file transfer, and profile features — all without using any database.

This project demonstrates practical implementation of:

TCP Client-Server Architecture

Socket Programming

GUI Development

Real-Time Communication

File Transfer using TCP



✨ Features

✔ Real-time messaging using TCP
✔ Attractive GUI interface
✔ Splash screen (2 seconds)
✔ Profile photo (circular display)
✔ Message bubbles (Sender message in Red)
✔ Private chat (Click user to view chat)
✔ File transfer option
✔ Same system multi-client support
✔ No database used







